{"tid":538544,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)加州大地震 千騙萬化","createTime":"2018-01-23T16:58:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-23T19:56:39.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bdabe65af57ab4810bd1f658a618f79a5a3e89a0","tid":538544,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T16:58:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=twUbOMYiiCgRTB8zOJLOKJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=969b5dbf\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=twUbOMYiiCgRTB8zOJLOKJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=00a41026\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/a/a3/San_Andreas_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fa%2Fa3%2FSan_Andreas_Poster.jpg&h=b4218845&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/f/fd/Focus_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Ff%2Ffd%2FFocus_Poster.jpg&h=3e403d5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.聲名狼藉的聖安德烈亞斯斷層終於崩塌之後，在加州引發了9級的大地震。負責搜尋救援的直昇機駕駛員雷&middot;蓋因斯（巨石強森 飾）與他失和的妻子艾瑪&middot;蓋因斯（卡拉&middot;古奇諾 飾）決定從洛杉磯往北飛向舊金山，一同搶救他們的小女兒布蕾克&middot;蓋因斯（亞歷珊卓&middot;達迪莉奧 飾）。然而，當他們以為早已度過最糟的情況時，危機四伏的驚險旅程其實才正要開始<br />\n<br />\n2.主要故事由詐騙老練技巧的尼基&middot;吉翁（威爾&middot;史密斯飾）走去夜總會一趟，遇上新手騙子傑斯&middot;芭蕾特（瑪歌&middot;羅比飾）為徒，之後進行向謝力源（黃榮亮飾）作為對賭。3年後，尼基&middot;吉翁成為格雷格（羅德里格&middot;桑托羅飾）賽車東主為下屬，期間再遇到傑斯&middot;芭蕾特為保持對方關係，後來被賽車東主識破後<br />\n<br />\n1 15AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=twUbOMYiiCgRTB8zOJLOKJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=734a10b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=twUbOMYiiCgRTB8zOJLOKJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=c5736a0e\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85b3b05a9cb386020e2a06b8ca56242737fe3db0","tid":538544,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T17:30:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35eed9e750bbffb5f8917e394aa169563a16cb47","tid":538544,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T18:22:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f287980dcc5b7233afed3d183d6961136d7c2408","tid":538544,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T18:48:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0268ee75e09261f6d8104cae4009dba10994563f","tid":538